{"tid":1096093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「金捲髮女」細膩高音逼哭觀眾 面具下竟是...","createTime":"2019-04-07T13:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T13:36:59.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26fbd593f1de9b87a2b39fef1b4ae679fb811e4a","tid":1096093,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"「金捲髮女」細膩高音逼哭觀眾 面具下竟是gu9udan金世正 <br />\n<br />\n南韓歌手金世正長相甜美、歌喉也很有實力，她從《PRODUCE 101》脫穎而出，先後成為女團I.O.I、gu9udan成員。她近日戴著金色捲髮女孩的面具匿名以名字「Iriga」亮相節目《蒙面歌王》，再次力證出眾的甜美歌喉，7日終於揭開面具下的真面目，令全場震驚不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4009/d4009978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4009%2Fd4009978.jpg&h=5e6b09b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金世正動人歌聲受到稱讚。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<br />\n金世正近來低調化身為「Iriga」，身穿粉紅色套裝、雙手戴著白手套，頂著金色捲髮的蝴蝶結甜美面具，隱藏身份做到滴水不漏，她3月底與「Gagamel」假面男合唱《I need you》，靠著甜蜜又清新的嗓音，擄獲全場觀眾，立刻掀起討問「Iriga到底是誰」，但也有早就猜到「應該是世正」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4009/d4009991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4009%2Fd4009991.jpg&h=89e6c901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼金世正揭下面具全場嚇一跳。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4009/d4009992.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4009%2Fd4009992.jpg&h=0769cee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4009/d4009980.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4009%2Fd4009980.jpg&h=5237dddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲智愛形容金世正的歌聲，感覺是令人很心疼的人。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相隔1個禮拜，「Iriga」7日出演節目《蒙面歌王》，接續帶來2首歌《致不再愛我的你》、《Twenty-five, Twenty-one》，動人的嗓音、細膩的高音驚豔全場，台下觀眾沈醉在她的傷感演唱裡，其中一位講評者Lovelyz智愛不捨表示：「感覺演唱者是令人心疼的年輕女孩。」雖然她在最後落選，但實力歌喉依舊受到認證，7日公開真實面貌，令全場露出驚訝表情，而這也是她自2017年後，2度挑戰《蒙面歌王》，她笑著表示：「心情輕鬆不少。」"},{"pid":"6c5f8a0833eb685b11e890982d0515ab511dfe2b","tid":1096093,"uid":46435,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"我都好能心痛她 jellyfish呢間死野真係執7左佢啦吊你老毋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66496568f8ae38f3d897e4e1b84b1dfd3731e832","tid":1096093,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"世正好似扮釘升物仙唱歌 跟住俾Once鬧..."},{"pid":"6c8e16ba853568301b94083a4b49f618b4fdac3d","tid":1096093,"uid":6908,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4009/d4009992.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4009%2Fd4009992.jpg&h=0769cee2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20703ad5c221decc300a601b8783ecc72b466a35","tid":1096093,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66496568f8ae38f3d897e4e1b84b1dfd3731e832","tid":1096093,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"世正好似扮釘升物仙唱歌 跟住俾Once鬧..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"IKON扮釘升物仙唱就聽過<br />\n有冇片😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"5dd32a451720cdc00c6d8da96773ffe0b838bbc4","tid":1096093,"uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20703ad5c221decc300a601b8783ecc72b466a35","tid":1096093,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66496568f8ae38f3d897e4e1b84b1dfd3731e832","tid":1096093,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"世正好似扮釘升物仙唱歌 跟住俾Once鬧..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"IKON扮釘升物仙唱就聽過<br />\n有冇片😂😂😂😂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lx92Cz7hppw?t=60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLx92Cz7hppw%3Ft%3D60&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=b2e35c40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lx92Cz7hppw?t=60</a>"},{"pid":"b2a505c1ddc3964acae113ad088ba